      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p176_s0004",
      "text": "Node_ or Fabric_Name",
      "bbox": [
        128.22,
        57.65,
        237.05,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p176_s0005",
      "text": "Node_Name is applicable to PLOGI, PLOGI LS_ACC and FLOGI.  Fabric_Name is applicable to",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        82.97,
        539.9,
        94.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p176_s0006",
      "text": "FLOGI LS_ACC.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        94.97,
        170.43,
        106.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p176_s0007",
      "text": "The Node_Name or Fabric_Name is an eight-byte field (words 7-8) that labels a Node or Fabric for",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        118.97,
        540.0,
        130.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p176_s0008",
      "text": "identification purposes, such as diagnostics., The Node_Name and Fabric_Name are independent of",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        130.97,
        540.04,
        142.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p176_s0009",
      "text": "and unrelated to network addressing. Each Node_Name or Fabric_Name shall be unique within the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        142.96,
        539.93,
        154.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p176_s0010",
      "text": "Fibre Channel interaction space . Bits 63-60 specify the format of the name. The formats are defined",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        154.96,
        540.05,
        166.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p176_s0011",
      "text": "in FC-FS-2.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        166.96,
        147.61,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
